high_descs: Turn left and head towards the right sink.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Take a step towards the sink on the left.
Place the fork inside the sink, wash it, and pick it up.
Place the fork on the counter at the edge of the sink with the potato in it.
anns.task_desc: Clean the fork from the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the fork from in front of the right sink basin.
Turn around, then go right, then turn to face the left sink basin.
Wash the fork in the sink.
Turn around, then face the left sink basin.
Place the fork on the counter, in front of the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork on the counter.

high_descs: Grab the fork by the sink
Walk to the left a bit
Put the fork in the sink on the left, turn on the faucet, wash the fork, turn off the faucet, take the fork out
Put the fork in front of the sink on the left
anns.task_desc: Wash the fork by the sink, put it in front of the left sink
